item.title: CVE-2021-1393|2024-08-03T16:11:17.083Z -- cisco -- cisco%20application%20services%20engine%20software
item.description: Multiple vulnerabilities in Cisco Application Services Engine could allow an unauthenticated, remote attacker to gain privileged access to host-level operations or to learn device-specific information, create diagnostic files, and make limited configuration changes. For more information about these vulnerabilities, see the Details section of this advisory.
